Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.67,0:01:10.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煎饼好好吃  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:10.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These pancakes are delicious, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这个甜甜的东西是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what do you call this sweet stuff?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是枫糖浆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's maple syrup
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多就像是从树上流下来的酱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's kinda like jelly that comes from trees
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树上流的酱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tree jelly?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.85,0:01:19.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:19.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gross
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.89,0:01:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宁愿现挤现吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I prefer mine on tap
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.10,0:01:28.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:28.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Bikini Bottom's
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.56,0:01:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一届植树节庆祝活动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,very first Arbor Day celebration
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.44,0:01:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,理发节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barber Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:33.03,注释,,0,0,0,,[ Barber（理发师）与 arbor（树木）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.03,0:01:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒挺需要稍微给头理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I could use a trim
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.40,0:01:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她说的应该是海港节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think she said Harbor Day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:37.45,注释,,0,0,0,,[ Harbor（海港）与 arbor（树木）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,专门给我这样的老海军庆功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to celebrate old Navy swabs like meself
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是植树节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Ar-bor Day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.12,0:01:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,专门庆祝植树喜悦的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a day to celebrate the joy of trees
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.37,0:01:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全裤头村就只有你有唯一一棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've got the only tree in town
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.67,0:01:51.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  只有我有树的日子已经到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:51.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Correction, I used to have the only tree
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为今天大家都可以自己种树了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause today you're all gonna grow your own tree
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海里长不出树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trees don't grow underwater
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.59,0:01:59.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些小家伙长得出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:01:59.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These little fellers will
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我利用科学的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've used the power of science
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.39,0:02:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,造出了可以长出海水树的特制橡子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make special acrons
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that will grow into saltwater trees
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  小树苗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, little tree
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.27,0:02:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.11,0:02:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能放嘴里嚼  你个榆木脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't need to chew it, you whittle stick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想保持树木健康  你们就只要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To keep your tree healthy, all you need to do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给树木多多施肥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is give it lots of fertilizer
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a problem
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One more thing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想长出全面发展的快乐小树
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to grow a happy, well-rounded tree
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得多跟树说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to talk to 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, little feller
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,测试  测试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Testing, testing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.02,0:02:47.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:47.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.98,0:02:54.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱向懂得保守秘密的人倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:54.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love talking to someone who knows how to keep a secret
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算可以跟别人说出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can finally tell someone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:58.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(982,198)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.57,0:03:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在贝壳城抢劫那会儿的事实真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what really happened
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I pulled that job in Shell City
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, little fella
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下就有不少人来跟你说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have lots of people talking to you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.29,0:03:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要找这里的老板谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would like to speak to the proprietor
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,投诉部门在那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The complaint department's over there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟那棵树说去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talk to the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:22.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1336,908)}投诉
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.92,0:03:22.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我蟹黄堡上的调料分配得太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the condiment distribution of my patty is subpar
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是跟树说话能让树长得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If talking to a tree is good for it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.60,0:03:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么抒情爵士一定会有奇效
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bet a little smooth jazz must be amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就用大自然的方式跟你说话好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to you the way nature intended
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让电视跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with television
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,456)}我的藤壶妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回到  我的藤壶妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We now return to “My Mother the Barnacle”
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love this one
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是可爱小树苗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a cutesy wittle tree?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想听睡前故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like to hear a bedtime story?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很久很久一段肥料以前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once upon a fertilizer
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有棵树妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there was a mama tree
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有棵树宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a baby tree
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有棵树爸爸去了森林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a papa tree who went out to the forest
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们突然碰见了伐木工小金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when they suddenly met little Goldy Lumberjack
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破故事一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a dumb story
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能给我闭嘴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you put a sock in it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要睡觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to get some shut-eye
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can talk?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要叫你小树皮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna name you Barky
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我放手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let go already
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.07,0:04:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都把我叶子给弄皱了  你个滤食怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're wrinkling my leaves, you filter feeding freak
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:29.58,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 海绵进食方式为滤食 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}过了一会儿
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那棵新树现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's your new tree doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有跟它说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you talking to it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽力了  不过实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying, but to be honest
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一句话都说不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really haven't been able to get a word in edgewise
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话全被我树给抢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My tree's been doing all the talking
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling okay, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.01,0:04:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小树皮想跟你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barky wants to talk to you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛要让我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you leave me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟这个傻笑带洞黄方块混一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with this giggling hunk o' holes?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他智力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's dimmer
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比停电期间半瓦功率的灯泡亮度还低
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than a half-watt bulb in a power outage
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真是个好家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, smack my tail and call me twitchy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我带杯水来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring me a glass of water
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我把土换掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Change my soil
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心别伤到根了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out for the roots
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你口气太臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your breath smells
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么只有脸没身体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you all face and no body?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.03,0:05:10.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:10.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doggy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这棵小树苗可真会聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This little shrub is a real chatterbox
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带我从这个垃圾场里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get me out of this dump
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这种敏感的小树苗得晒太阳才能活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sensitive tree like me needs sun
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too cold out here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太阳太亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sun is too bright
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我拿毛衣过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody get me a sweater
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要回房里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to go back inside
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要造出来的是海水树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make saltwater trees
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这棵树攻击性也太强太嗨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but this one's a bit too salty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道其他人的树怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how everyone else's trees are doing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.94,0:05:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不该让这树开船的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have let him drive
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码泡芙老师挺高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least Mrs. Puff is having a good time
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个蟹黄堡太难吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but this Krabby Patty tastes awful
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你太难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you look awful
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我不会向你抗议的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you don't hear me complaining
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冒犯到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am offended
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And offensive
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心  什么味道那么臭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,PU, what stinks?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边到底是来客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that the customers
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是收垃圾的开始送外卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or has the garbage man started making deliveries?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里本来还好端端的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This used to be a respectable place
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.43,0:06:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都在抗议我投诉部门搞抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People are complaining about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me complaint department complaining
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音这么难听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that horrible noise?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你该把那玩意登记成致命武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should register that thing as a lethal weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.23,0:06:24.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天赋不是万能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talent isn't everything
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这种情况就是无能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In your case, it's nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.87,0:06:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回到  海胆哥与败蜗子秀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now back to "The Sir Urchin & Snail Fail Show"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:40.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,228)}海胆哥与败蜗子秀
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才一天年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just one day old
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都知道就只有小屁孩才看这节目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and even I can see this show is for babies
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get what?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.98,0:07:07.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out you go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兜风兜完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This joyride is over
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思是我没驾照了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this mean I don't get my license?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  警察局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, police department?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有贝壳城抢劫案的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a lead on that Shell City job
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你理发师打电话过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, your barber called
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说他对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said he's sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,庸俗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Philistine
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小的们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起开心玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's have some fun
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  等我先洗完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, wait your turn
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放松
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Relax
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样可以帮你们长得又大又壮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This will help you grow big and strong
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, chump
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她在那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There she is
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,植树节大乱都是她害的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Arbor Day anarchy is all her fault
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那群树大肆搞破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those trees are ruining everything
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta go
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那群树浑身是木头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're made of wood
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建议直接烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say we burn them
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.27,0:09:03.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:03.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, burn 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.77,0:09:09.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  这样不是植树节的精神所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:09.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, that's not the spirit of Arbor Day
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.23,0:09:11.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都别急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:11.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone, calm down
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a plan
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.91,0:09:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎大家前来观赏树木大聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come one, come all to Log-a-palooza
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.96,0:09:30.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是欢庆植树节的盛大表演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:30.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an Arbor Day extravaganza
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有肥料可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you can eat fertilizer
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树木可以免费到场观看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're a tree, you get in free
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们树根是不是发皱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are your roots too wrinkly?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们树叶是不是发蔫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are your leaves feeling wilted?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我树皮摸着有点粗糙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bark is feeling a little rough
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就来试用一下我的神奇美容机器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then try my wonderful makeover machine
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树木复苏机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Arbor Revitalizer
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过植树节也得美美的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look your best this Arbor Day
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁要自愿上台来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I have any volunteers?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我这就试用一下你那个破铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll give your dumb machine a try
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃  保叶要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for your leaves
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家先别走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone wait
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来命中注定要烂在林中一角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was destined to rot in the woods somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在看看我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but look at me now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我变椅子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a chair
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.90,0:10:35.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,身体从来没感觉这么光滑过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:35.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never felt so smooth
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他样子确实挺帅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He does look pretty handsome
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也想变椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be a chair, too
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想变柜子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be a credenza
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想变锯木架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be a sawhorse
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想变桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be a table
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要下一个  我要下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me next, me next
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们椅子真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These guys are great
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你办法想得真好  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thinking, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把树变家具真的让树不闹腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Furniturizing really calmed these trees down
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.44,0:11:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  椅子最强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, chairs rule
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码大多数还是不闹腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, most of them anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明年还是不过植树节好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'll skip Arbor Day next year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.87,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFA3&}窃牙记
