Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(757.802,488)}客串
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又过了美好的一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just had another great--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.77,0:11:48.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:48.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.93,0:11:52.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我长鼻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:52.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm growing a nose
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.22,0:11:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不要鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want a nose
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.17,0:11:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你掉了一颗牙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just lost a tooth
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上把牙齿放枕头底下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if you put that tooth under your pillow tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牙仙子就会过来取走牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Tooth Fairy with come and take the tooth
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.30,0:12:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后给你留下两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and leave you a quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.65,0:12:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一颗牙值两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A quarter for just one tooth?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jackpot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}当晚
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  牙牙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, teethies
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.10,0:12:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,犯罪生活就是回报多多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who says a life of crime doesn't pay?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.83,0:13:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡拳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sleep punch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:13.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(716,358)}多余闪粉
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁往那走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是牙仙子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Tooth Fairy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要给海绵宝宝看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta show SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.00,0:13:30.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:30.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were right
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.72,0:13:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牙仙子过来了  我还抓到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Tooth Fairy came, and I got him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没偷东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you-you-
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的抓到了牙仙子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you really did catch the Tooth Fairy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told ya
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.62,0:14:15.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他没给我两毛五  不过你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:15.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He didn't give me a quarter, but look
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.08,0:14:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在他袋子里发现了奇珍异宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found these precious jewels in his bag
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩白痴在唠叨什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you chowderheads yapping about?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还什么牙仙子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tooth Fairy?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没必要对着咱俩装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to play dumb with us
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你秘密不会暴露的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your secret is safe
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚带我们跟你一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please let us ride along with you tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.02,0:14:33.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让咱当你的牙仙子小助手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:33.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And be your Tooth Fairy assistants
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是牙仙子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Tooth Fairy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要有人来帮我趁火打劫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I could use a little help scoring loot--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.17,0:14:46.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  收集牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:46.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, collecting teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.25,0:14:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚一定很漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be a long night
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.87,0:15:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里一定可以找到牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet we could find some teeth here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.75,0:15:05.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:05.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pull over
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位老是喝汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, this guy drinks a lot of soda
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定有几颗松动的牙齿可以取走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I'm sure he's got a few loose teeth for us
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get him
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.36,0:15:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  戴上特制牙仙子面罩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, use these special Tooth Fairy masks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.55,0:16:01.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太不专业了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:01.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amateurs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.28,0:16:03.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  是海霸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:03.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, it's Bubble--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.53,0:16:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你们两个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, why don't you mugs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.77,0:16:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到这位小个子的身上找牙齿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,shake down Tiny here for some teeth?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.35,0:16:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到那边那堆贵重物品去找牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna look for teeth in those valuables over there
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有牙仙子才可以这么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the Tooth Fairy gets to laugh like that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.85,0:16:26.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没摸到牙齿  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:26.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't feel any teeth, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我摸到了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I feel a bunch of them
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这颗好松
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one's really loose
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.22,0:16:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱帮忙拔出来  牙仙子一定不会介意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Tooth Fairy won't mind if we help it out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacle Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.26,0:17:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放别人枕头底下的钱原来存这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this where you keep the pillow money?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牙齿最近还挺值钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Teeth are sure worth a lot these days
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  去找更多牙齿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get more teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的工作最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got the best job ever
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:41.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1602,926)}贝臂
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.65,0:18:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.47,0:18:35.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个白痴今晚帮了牙仙子不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stooges really gave the Tooth Fairy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a lot of help tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你们害我很头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even if you also gave me a headache
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like helping
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.81,0:18:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱还有时间最后再来抢一家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I think we got time for one last job if you're in
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板就住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's where Mr. Krabs lives
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.46,0:18:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是我白天的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's my daytime boss
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我晚上的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my nighttime boss
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.55,0:19:05.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:05.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch out for booby traps
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.95,0:19:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我帮蟹老板安装了安保系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I helped Mr. Krabs install the security system myself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.33,0:19:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.92,0:19:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里就有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's one
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,326)}拉我
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.80,0:19:13.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来解除警报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:13.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll disarm it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.11,0:19:16.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:16.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.89,0:19:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在楼下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's down there?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm calling the police
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警察吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, police?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.00,0:19:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come quick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.82,0:19:22.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听到有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:22.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard a noise
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.85,0:19:24.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好  吵醒蟹老板了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:24.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, we woke him up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.89,0:19:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们到底是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the name of Poseidon's pantaloons are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.10,0:19:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们为什么触发了我的小偷警报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why have you tripped me burglar alarm?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们为什么背着小偷袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why do you have those burglar sacks?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们为什么戴着小偷面罩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why are you wearing burglar masks?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们为什么跟着那个小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why are you with that burglar?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是小偷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you burglars?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.41,0:19:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份加了奶酪的小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take a burglar with cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not burglars
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是在给牙仙子当助手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We were just assisting the Tooth Fairy here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是牙仙子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ain't no Tooth Fairy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.40,0:20:06.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我几年前就把牙齿全卖给真牙仙子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:06.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sold all my teeth to the real Tooth Fairy years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.44,0:20:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了  警察来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, the fuzz
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们快帮我逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gotta get me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板说你不是真牙仙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs says you're not the real Tooth Fairy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.70,0:20:16.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然是真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:16.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I am
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们一定要相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just gotta believe
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.90,0:20:21.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:21.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's all, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.75,0:20:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我相信你  牙仙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe in you, Tooth Fairy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们两个也太好骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those two are so gullible
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:41.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,336)}拉我
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绳子上面写  拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This rope says "pull me"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能再往前走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't go any farther
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The jig is up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.53,0:21:06.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是牙仙子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:06.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a Tooth Fairy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can fly
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.77,0:21:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞向安全地带
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fly to safety
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.49,0:21:10.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:10.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fly
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了带上牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.75,0:21:23.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or your boat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我好像感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Patrick, I get the feeling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是真牙仙子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that wasn't the real Tooth Fairy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I am
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.67,0:21:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真牙仙子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The real Tooth Fairy?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.86,0:21:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们整晚都在努力收集牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two did a wonderful job collecting teeth all night
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.65,0:21:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此  我要让你们成为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:47.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I'm going to make you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.20,0:21:50.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牙仙子名誉小助手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:50.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,honorary Tooth Fairy assistants
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿瓦达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Abraca--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.32,0:21:53.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,索牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:53.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dental
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧
